      "content": "i get that, but i already checked my levels and they're on the lower side right now. i'm just worried about waking up at 3am with a massive hypoglycemic episode because i didn't eat enough to offset the basal. if i just skip it tonight, wouldn't that actually be the safer move to avoid a crash?",
